oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Coors Light Logo
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Logos (Symbols);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Four black and white halftone different sized images of the Coors Light logo. In each of the logos, the word "light" has been crossed out with a pen. One of the versions was probably used to create a metal photoplate.
